    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <opener>
                        <placeName>[Down.]</placeName>
                    </opener>
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>The facts which you relate about the phascolarctos are very surprising, and I will carefully preserve your note for use on some future occasion.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            
            
            
            
            
            <div type="footnotes">
                <note xml:id="foot.f1">The date range is established by the relationship between this letter and the letters from Arthur Nicols, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7553.xml">7 March 1871</ref> and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7570.xml">11 March 1871</ref> (<hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi> vol. 19).</note>
                <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi> vol. 19, letter from Arthur Nicols, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7553.xml">7 March 1871</ref>. Nicols had written about pet koalas (<hi rend="italic">Phascolarctos cinereus</hi>) that acquired a taste for tobacco and rum.</note>
            </div>
        
